<asp:Content ID="Content2" ContentPlaceHolderID="maincontentplaceholder" runat="server">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <div class="card-header">
                <h2>This is the online aptitute test system application</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <p>In this project, we are going to make an online interview system where an manager can take interview for the current candidate who are logged in this system. Here, the manager will take the interview of objective type questions.</p>
                <p>In manager section </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>An admin can add another admin</li>
                    <li>An admin can add manager and other staff</li>
                    <li>An manager can create criteria type</li>
                    <li>An manager can add criteria question with multiple object with answer</li>
                    <li>An manager can see a candidate result as well as profile</li>
                    <li>An manager can reset his/her profile</li>
                </ul>
                <p>In candidate section </p>
                <p>&nbsp;</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>A candidate can create his profile </li>
                    <li>A candidate can take part in interview </li>
                    <li>A candidate can search the website to get easilt the interview</li>
                    <li>A candidate can see his progress report</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
